📘 Confluence Page: NimbusApp Server Troubleshooting Guide – Frontend, Backend, DB Nodes

(Slug: playbooks/nimbusapp-server-troubleshooting)

⸻

🧠 Summary

This playbook provides actionable steps to resolve common server issues across the NimbusApp architecture — including frontend (UI/API), backend (processing/services), and database (RDS/PostgreSQL) nodes.

This content is indexed for the NimbusOps Chatbot, which can answer contextually with specific command-line instructions and AWS console navigation.

